metrics_conclusion: Ring 6 - LoTown has higher complexity than the average song  in terms Melodic Complexity, Chord-Melody Tension and Chord-Bass Melody.
key_conclusion: Ring 6 - LoTown has sections analyzed in the following keys: E♭ Major, C Major,  and F♯ Minor.  Click on the linked cheat sheets for popular chords, chord progressions, downloadable midi files and more!

metadata.editComments: For those who may argue that this is a bVI - bVII - i progression, I hear you and that is valid, however it is also wrong >:) especially given the big fat Eb Major chord we get during the climax in the outro.
Accidentally got rid of the lydian key changes, put them back.
Changed most of the vi chords to IVmaj7 chords and the I chords to a Imaj7 chords. Reflections upon further in-depth listening.
